dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. The title cartouche includes branches of fruit and is topped with a vase of flowers and fruit. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map 36 x 47 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Vignaud, Henry, 1830-1922, former owner, Composite Atlas of France.
